"title": "6022: sin, causes of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6022: sin, causes of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Sin is the result of the fall, at which the creation rebels against God its Creator.</p>\n<h2>Sin as a result of the devil's activity</h2>\n<h3>The devil's instigation of the first sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:13\">GEN 3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1-Gen3:6\">GEN 3:1–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:3\">2CO 11:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:9\">REV 12:9</a></p>\n<h3>The devil's role as tempter</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:5\">1TH 3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:1-Matt4:11\">MAT 4:1–4:11</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:12-Mark1:13\">MRK 1:12–1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:1-Luke4:13\">LUK 4:1–4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:13\">MAT 6:13</a></p>\n<h3>The devil as the source of sinful behaviour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:44\">JHN 8:44</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:38\">JHN 8:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:41\">JHN 8:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:8\">1JN 3:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:10\">1JN 3:10</a></p>\n<h3>The sins of angels</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:4\">2PE 2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:6\">JUD 1:6</a></p>\n<h2>Sin as a power in the world</h2>\n<h3>Sin's reign from the time of Adam</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12\">ROM 5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:7\">GEN 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:34\">JHN 8:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:21\">ROM 5:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:16\">ROM 6:16</a></p>\n<h3>Sin uses the law to provoke sinful desires</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:5\">ROM 7:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:7-Rom7:12\">ROM 7:7–7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:56\">1CO 15:56</a></p>\n<h3>The world is under sin's dominion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:16\">1JN 2:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:34\">LUK 21:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:12\">TIT 2:12</a></p>\n<h2>Sin is rooted in human nature</h2>\n<h3>The human heart is dominated by sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:9\">JER 17:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:19\">MAT 15:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:21-Mark7:22\">MRK 7:21–7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:24\">ROM 1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:12\">HEB 3:12</a></p>\n<h3>Human nature is fundamentally opposed to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:5-Rom8:8\">ROM 8:5–8:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:14-Rom7:25\">ROM 7:14–7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:17-Gal5:21\">GAL 5:17–5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:3\">EPH 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:10\">2PE 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:18\">2PE 2:18</a></p>\n<h2>The act of sinning</h2>\n<h3>Sin results from giving in to evil desires</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:14-Jas1:15\">JAS 1:14–1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:13-Rom13:14\">ROM 13:13–13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:1\">JAS 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:16\">JUD 1:16</a></p>\n<h3>Sin results from the human desire to be like God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:5\">GEN 3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:12-Isa14:14\">ISA 14:12–14:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:2\">EZK 28:2</a></p>\n<h3>Sin results when the body is placed at sin's disposal</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:13\">ROM 6:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:29-Matt5:30\">MAT 5:29–5:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:8-Matt18:9\">MAT 18:8–18:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:43-Mark9:47\">MRK 9:43–9:47</a></p>\n<h3>Sin results from the influence of others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:33\">1CO 15:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:33\">EXO 23:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:3\">1KI 11:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:10\">PRO 1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:24-Prov22:25\">PRO 22:24–22:25</a></p>\n<h3>The seriousness of leading others into sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:42\">MRK 9:42</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:6\">MAT 18:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:1-Luke17:2\">LUK 17:1–17:2</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:9-1Cor8:13\">1CO 8:9–8:13</a></p>",
